    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>暑假终于来了，我很高兴。我想好好享受这段时间，做一些有趣的事情。这是我的暑假记录，我会在这里分享我的经历~</p><span id="more"></span><h2 id="厨房里"><a href="#厨房里" class="headerlink" title="厨房里"></a>厨房里</h2><h3 id="回锅肉"><a href="#回锅肉" class="headerlink" title="回锅肉"></a>回锅肉</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E5%9B%9E%E9%94%85%E8%82%891.jpg" alt="回锅肉"></p><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E5%9B%9E%E9%94%85%E8%82%892.jpg" alt="回锅肉"></p><h3 id="炒面"><a href="#炒面" class="headerlink" title="炒面"></a>炒面</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E7%82%92%E9%9D%A2.jpg" alt="炒面"></p><h3 id="煎饺"><a href="#煎饺" class="headerlink" title="煎饺"></a>煎饺</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E7%85%8E%E9%A5%BA1.jpg" alt="煎饺"></p><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E7%85%8E%E9%A5%BA2.jpg" alt="煎饺"></p><h3 id="鸡丝茭白"><a href="#鸡丝茭白" class="headerlink" title="鸡丝茭白"></a>鸡丝茭白</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E9%B8%A1%E4%B8%9D%E8%8C%AD%E7%99%BD.jpg" alt="鸡丝茭白"></p><h3 id="酱油牛肉"><a href="#酱油牛肉" class="headerlink" title="酱油牛肉"></a>酱油牛肉</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E9%85%B1%E6%B2%B9%E7%89%9B%E8%82%89.jpg" alt="酱油牛肉"></p><h3 id="咖喱土豆鸡肉"><a href="#咖喱土豆鸡肉" class="headerlink" title="咖喱土豆鸡肉"></a>咖喱土豆鸡肉</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%86%E9%B8%A1%E8%82%891.jpg" alt="咖喱土豆鸡肉"></p><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E5%92%96%E5%96%B1%E5%9C%9F%E8%B1%86%E9%B8%A1%E8%82%892.jpg" alt="咖喱土豆鸡肉"></p><h3 id="芹菜豆腐干"><a href="#芹菜豆腐干" class="headerlink" title="芹菜豆腐干"></a>芹菜豆腐干</h3><p><img src="https://raw.gitmirror.com/WindsorWu/Blog_Photo/master/2023/06/18/%E8%8A%B9%E8%8F%9C%E8%B1%86%E8%85%90